melka.echonest
Class ENTrack

java.lang.Object
  melka.echonest.ENTrack

public class ENTrack
extends java.lang.Object

Contains global estimated information, applicable to the whole track. Note that because local data may vary in the course of the track, this global estimation may not apply well to certain sections of the music.

Author:
melka
